results.title: Dolan Creek Retreat—Big Sur
results.text: Sunny, treehouse-like master bedroom suite with fireplace, king size bed in elegant Castro district home. Your private third floor suite overlooks a lush and peaceful garden and patio. Renovated spa-like bathroom with soaking tub and slate floors, fluffy towels, and access to atrium/sun room and library/den with satellite tv. Wireless internet. Safe and friendly neighborhood in central SF location.
